cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper explores the behavior of a convolutional neural net in a continual-learning setting for visual classification tasks, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, since the focus is primarily on machine learning and computer vision, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely categories, followed by cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.CL.
